{"tid":791820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《時代》刊白宮辦公室「水浸」三步曲　最新封面特朗普掙扎求存","createTime":"2018-08-24T06:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T23:55:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f038b4070d9b30fff52777ce9f3b267b2b356985","tid":791820,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180824/s00005/25581febcb6db768c098605eab205a88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180824%2Fs00005%2F25581febcb6db768c098605eab205a88.jpg&h=249086d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普的兩名前心腹，私人律師科恩及前競選經理馬納福特，分別承認違反競選法，及被判8項銀行欺詐與稅務欺詐等罪成。新一期《時代》雜誌再次以特朗普作封面人物，聯同去年2月和今年4月的封面，形容特朗普的政治危機已去到快將他淹沒的地步。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》雜誌早於特朗普去年1月上任後，在2月的封面以〈Nothing to See Here〉為題，看到特朗普氣定神閒地坐在白宮橢圓形辦公室，風雨交加以致桌上文件、領呔和頭髮都飛起來，當時文章形容他上任不足一個月，白宮已出現混亂。<br />\n<br />\n直至今年4月，雜誌以同一圖片再稍作改動，顯示白宮的暴風雨已導致出現辦公室水浸，惟受「艷星門」事件纏繞的特朗普的神情未有絲毫轉變。在公布該封面前，剛發生聯邦調查局突襲科恩的辦公室一事，當局調查內容包括科恩向色情電影女艷星克利福德（Stephanie Clifford）的匯款記錄。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》雜誌周四（23日）公布新一期封面，成為上述兩期的後續，特朗普需在幾乎被完全淹浸的辦公室中掙扎求存，抬頭到水面呼吸。創作三幅作品的奧布賴恩（Tim O'Brien）表示，最新封面的關鍵是特朗普還能否安於辦公桌上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180824/s00005/1535084207358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180824%2Fs00005%2F1535084207358&d=XyYT95eQ3mbSuwd14sle%2BW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f4765014\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180824%2Fs00005%2F1535084207358&h=75c5e63d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180824/s00005/1535084207358</a>"},{"pid":"b1e4c0549999f01ab7e0c93f4ea0c229248dd008","tid":791820,"uid":34444,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"Fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad5883fb260672ec93cbd8f0782785190ea7a96","tid":791820,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"a28f5002b193a39a6e12793c4e1d5a5629284db1","tid":791820,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIPf1BaBDILVxbYA/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIPf1BaBDILVxbYA%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=5e165d00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cb9993a128623f6b4dec87e4c6fda8c3ba4ce66","tid":791820,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"而家時代超級bias"},{"pid":"2ca6975077e57d19e3acae981df122d899da3e19","tid":791820,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://patriot.imgix.net/72c99f52a9bad711e761bb74689e6af52b83490a291871945692b366a03f6700.jpg?auto=format\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpatriot.imgix.net%2F72c99f52a9bad711e761bb74689e6af52b83490a291871945692b366a03f6700.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat&h=1b21bb14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"584b2f40118e49911670855dfa52b6a94919a359","tid":791820,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3cb9993a128623f6b4dec87e4c6fda8c3ba4ce66","tid":791820,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"而家時代超級bias"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"出盡力去奶支"},{"pid":"59eeec135db468cd2e62da3719a6dcc925ee3202","tid":791820,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb9993a128623f6b4dec87e4c6fda8c3ba4ce66","tid":791820,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"而家時代超級bias"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"keyword：時代高層 支那 貪腐"},{"pid":"cc2d54b7078b4e48748097712fa3110d116e79d4","tid":791820,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"Trump上場梗係亂啦<br />\n人哋根本唔係民主共和兩黨打滾多年嘅專業政棍<br />\n選舉資金大部分用自己賺返嚟嘅錢，唔係靠既有利益者嘅財團捐款<br />\n上場對住呢班專業政棍，既有利益嘅扯線公仔，個局唔亂至奇<br />\n因為人哋根本冇需要聽你哋支笛<br />\n<br />\n相反成班已經被利益控制嘅傳媒，至Trump上場以來根本冇停過，喺到盲反Trump<br />\n佢哋係真正嘅盲反，唔係連登成日講嗰種「盲反」<br />\n連喺Twitter每日幾百個tweet打錯一隻字covefe都要打飛機鬧成個禮拜<br />\n呢本Time magazine仲要原本個名有權威，都要無中生有整個fake news封面嚟打飛機<br />\n<br />\n冇眼睇！"},{"pid":"65cea59a4268063b0dd204defbad042b340c8094","tid":791820,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T23:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c14f88ce57ba58c4222deb63519b0993c0c3799","tid":791820,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"5528b61ea0e3d6dcf4125fa213a6cf6f4e2b6a72","tid":791820,"uid":169435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T23:55:43.000Z","msg":"除非侵侵貪污<br />\n否則冇可能比人拉到落台"}]}